# 4. **Terms of Trade: The Single Most Important AUD Driver**

Terms of trade (TOT) = Export prices / Import prices
Australia = exports **iron ore, coal, LNG**, imports **manufactures**.

![Image](https://d3fy651gv2fhd3.cloudfront.net/charts/australia-exports-of-iron-ore-concentrates.png?h=400\&ismobile=1\&lbl=0\&s=auexioca\&v=202404061100V20230410\&w=640\&utm_source=chatgpt.com)

