# 🇦🇺 **AUSTRALIA: FUNDING RATE STRUCTURE & LIQUIDITY TRANSMISSION MECHANISM**

![Image](https://www.rba.gov.au/education/images/explainers/the-australian-cash-rate.png?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

![Image](https://www.investopedia.com/thmb/OBKNUY88WSCRnU8cHb_G7XfADTE%3D/1500x0/filters%3Ano_upscale%28%29%3Amax_bytes%28150000%29%3Astrip_icc%28%29/vdotdash_INV_final-The-Foreign-Exchange-Interbank-Market_Feb_2021-01-bb2f378cd30b4e52903c2dc382c1121d.jpg?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

